snippet.title: Flow Fox Demo is now live!
snippet.description:
Flow Fox is a fast paced precision platformer game, with some foddian elements to it. You start outside and must run across the scenary to the entrance, where you then must climb across different terrains that will demand you to be fast, precise, and think!

Try it here: https://afkabi.itch.io/flow-fox
